{"tid":1414941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】聽日再罷工","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:31:06.000Z","uid":67232,"like":11,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8958e959be428a361602f0f6819c935b9b6ab3a2","tid":1414941,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"罷工點會淨係罷得嗰一日呀?真係咁樣嘅話，我送你一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日太陽照舊升起</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日d狗癲咗咁開催淚彈放題，聽日仲返工?罷工淨係罷得嗰一日，我係林鄭都指住你哋嚟笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但真心前線唔好再只係抱住一種心態:<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">我今日嚟係為咗打狗</span><br />\n而係必要時以武制暴，有事一齊企出嚟，和平時份一齊撚撚狗，唔好比仇恨支配自己。<br />\n<br />\n罷完去邊我唔知，但大家唔好集結埋一齊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，犯法架，比人告非法集結架。<br />\n<br />\n利申:反對任何犯法嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ccb0926e4191c64e69b3846ece2a1207588269","tid":1414941,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"永不割蓆"},{"pid":"4116497c5a04480576a020ebf70ee654bcc3bae5","tid":1414941,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"唔好非法集結呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17458defbe37c82c2d273087cc7fa341d01ed205","tid":1414941,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"會比狗狗追架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09fc380713c57ddc70e89b675035412e313e814","tid":1414941,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:09:09.000Z","msg":"睇完幫下手推，再出去推返現場post啦"},{"pid":"44ee65bb53abf16076af8d6cd1108ad7bcba898f","tid":1414941,"uid":192697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"地鐵真係好撚易。。。。一二百條友。。。成條線玩撚完"},{"pid":"aa3e31471d6f88fe98d8fbaef8bca7bebc4abece","tid":1414941,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:13:51.000Z","msg":"今日都未搞掂,邊有咁快 籌備到聽朝"},{"pid":"04499dd776ca1f64c77c941c2b41b33773e8f88a","tid":1414941,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fe8245a019a8a406c3f9694230d6d0e171bf2a9","tid":1414941,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99efc98d18aef148653f13b344c6e2fb7d8b0d1e","tid":1414941,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:25:48.000Z","msg":"唔係你話罷就罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港共對私人機構罷工，一向都 WFC。<br />\n<br />\n只有影響到機場 (今日港共收晒口)，對海外運輸，佢地先會驚。"},{"pid":"6708c4b56c5080f109be945f0c5a086f271e3a3e","tid":1414941,"uid":25367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"真心應該抖抖先，一嚟冇時間宣傳冇人知要罷，二嚟聽日再示威就係連續第四日，大部分人都頂唔順<br />\n最好依家開始宣傳下星期罷一日，然後政府都唔答應五大訴求就再下星期罷兩日"},{"pid":"091396db67d7579eff9b13e482b229b4f4e4bbd2","tid":1414941,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"emmmm chur過龍wo"}]}